Project: Ticket Parser Service

Version: v1.0
Owner: Backend Automation System

1️⃣ Overview
1.1 Purpose

The Ticket Parser Service is a backend microservice responsible for:

Listening to a Gmail inbox

Detecting flight ticket emails

Extracting email body and/or PDF attachment

Parsing structured airline ticket data

Forwarding structured data to the Query Parser System

Marking the email as read only after successful processing

This service does NOT generate the final agency ticket.
That responsibility belongs to the Query Parser System.

2️⃣ High-Level Architecture
Gmail Inbox
    ↓
Polling Listener (every 30 sec)
    ↓
Unread Email Fetch
    ↓
Ticket Detection
    ↓
Extract Content (PDF > Body)
    ↓
LLM Ticket Parser
    ↓
Backend Calculations
    ↓
Forward to Query Parser System
    ↓
Mark Email as Read
